'''沙伊拉特空軍基地'''（{{airport codes|||OS65}}）為[[敘利亞空軍|敘利亞空軍]]位於[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]的基地，沙伊拉特空軍基地有两条跑道及約40座硬式掩蔽部。常驻有一下三个飞行中队：
*第675飞行中队（[[米格-23战斗机|米格-23战斗机]]）
*第677飞行中队（[[Su-17攻擊機|Su-22攻击机]]）
*第687飞行中队（Su-22攻击机）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.scramble.nl/orbats/syria/airforce|title=Scramble|website=www.scramble.nl|access-date=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407234328/http://www.scramble.nl/orbats/syria/airforce|dead-url=no}}</ref>

美国称此空军机场有[[化学武器|化学武器]]的储备。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Strategy-Policy Mismatch: How the U.S. Army Can Help Close Gaps in Countering Weapons of Mass Destruction|url=https://archive.org/details/strategypolicymi0000bond|last=Bonds|first=Timothy|last2=Larson|first2=Eric|last3=Eaton|first3=Derek|last4=Darilek|first4=Richard|publisher=RAND Arroyo Center|year=2014|isbn=978-0-8330-8631-0|location=http://www.dtic.mil/docs/citations/ADA609703|pages=[https://archive.org/details/strategypolicymi0000bond/page/n110 110]}}</ref>

俄罗斯空军也使用此基地的设施。2015年，俄罗斯曾扩建该机场以起降俄罗斯飞机。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rferl.org/a/russia-expanding-second-syrian-air-base-near-islamic-state/27406249.html|title=Russia Expanding Second Syrian Air Base Near IS-Held Areas|last=|first=|date=December 4, 2015|work=RadioFreeEurope|access-date=7 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407233856/http://www.rferl.org/a/russia-expanding-second-syrian-air-base-near-islamic-state/27406249.html|archive-date=2017-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年2月，俄罗斯增加了该机场武装直升机的数量。简氏防务杂志称，该基地有4架Mi-25直升机（[[Mi-24雌鹿直升機|Mi-24雌鹿直升機]]的衍生型号），4架Mi-24直升机和一架[[Mi-8直升機|Mi-8/17直升機]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://search.proquest.com/docview/1767826269?accountid=10920|title=Russia increases support for syrian offensive against islamic state.|last=Ripley|first=Tim|date=Feb 24, 2016|work=Jane's Defence Weekly|access-date=7 april 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502054542/https://search.proquest.com/docview/1767826269?accountid=10920|archive-date=2019-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==2017年空袭==
{{main article|2017年沙伊拉特打击行动}}
2017年4月7日，[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]期间，美国海军从位于[[地中海|地中海]]的伯克级驱逐舰上发射了59枚[[战斧巡航导弹|战斧巡航导弹]]，打击沙伊拉特空军基地。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.defense.gov/News/News-Releases/News-Release-View/Article/1144598/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria|title=Statement from Pentagon Spokesman Capt. Jeff Davis on U.S. strike in S|work=U.S. DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE|access-date=2017-04-07|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407071200/https://www.defense.gov/News/News-Releases/News-Release-View/Article/1144598/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美国中央司令部|美国中央司令部]]在随后向媒体发出消息，行动摧毁了空军基地的战机，防御机库，石油和后勤储备，弹药库，机场防空系统和雷达。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.centcom.mil/MEDIA/PRESS-RELEASES/Press-Release-View/Article/1144711/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria/|title=Statement from Pentagon Spokesman Capt. Jeff Davis on U.S. strike in Syria|last=|first=|date=7 April 2017|website=U.S. Central Command|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407233354/http://www.centcom.mil/MEDIA/PRESS-RELEASES/Press-Release-View/Article/1144711/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria/|archive-date=2017-04-07|dead-url=yes|access-date=7 April 2017}}</ref>一家俄罗斯电视台称，有9架飞机被摧毁，当时应该没有飞机在执行任务。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2017-04-07/syrian-planes-out-of-action-at-time-of-us-strike-on-airfield/|title=Nine Syrian planes destroyed by US strike on airfield|publisher=ITV News|date=7 April 2017|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407234043/http://www.itv.com/news/update/2017-04-07/syrian-planes-out-of-action-at-time-of-us-strike-on-airfield/|dead-url=no}}</ref>叙利亚政府方面的报告统计，共有16人在这次袭击中死亡，其中7人为叙利亚士兵。<ref name="wsj_casualties">{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/syrian-media-say-u-s-attack-caused-damage-to-air-base-multiple-casualties-1491535071|title=Syria Says Strike Kills 16, Damages Air Base|first1=Raja|last1=Abdulrahim|first2=Noam|last2=Rydan|date=7 April 2017|publisher=|via=www.wsj.com|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408060626/https://www.wsj.com/articles/syrian-media-say-u-s-attack-caused-damage-to-air-base-multiple-casualties-1491535071|dead-url=no}}</ref>

